flowchart LR
    Request["1. request\ncreate ApprovalRequest and notify a human"] --> Wait["2. wait\npause for decision within policy timeout"]
    Wait -->|approved| Execute["3. execute_if_approved\nrun the side-effecting action"]
    Wait -->|rejected| Reject["Return rejected + reason"]
    Wait -->|timed out| Timeout["Escalate or cancel\naccording to policy"]
    Execute --> Log["4. log\nrequest, decision, result"]
    Reject --> Log
    Timeout --> Log

    style Request fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
    style Wait fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    style Execute fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    style Log fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825
